個陣10號個累積數量係704990<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=deb3a36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19:13個陣10號個累積數量係757943<br />\n<br />\n總時間長度=19:13-17:42=91秒<br />\n數量增長=757943-704990=52953<br />\n增長速率=52953/91=582/秒<br />\n<br />\n根據賽前BBC記錄 10號同9號有明顯差距<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c861a540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10號同9號差距=1768205-698644=1069561<br />\n<br />\n假設10號一直保持同一個速率去追<br />\n假設9號當晚完全冇增長<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10號超越9號所需時間=1069561/582=1838秒=31分鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n成個環節頭尾應該冇30分鐘 仲要未計9號當晚個增長 <br />\n完全睇唔到10號會贏個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<strong>蘋果日報--【唔公平?】超專業分析 網友 : 最受歡迎港姐無可能係張寶欣</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/bBrel3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FbBrel3&d=5v2X%2F3V4BzXuJH62QZmuu8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fdf20ddc\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/bBrel3</a><br />\n<br />\n今年香港小姐競選決賽不斷Hard Sell大台直播App，就連友誼小姐一獎都改做「big big channel最受歡迎香港小姐」。此獎項以直播App上網友給的心心作標準，稱以最高心心數量的佳麗奪得，最後獎項由10號張寶欣獲得。先不論有大量網友投訴直播App在比賽其間完全不能開啟，既然這麼多人未能連線，那心心從哪裡來可說是個迷。賽前被網友極力支持的9號金美黎，不但三甲不入，就連「BBC最受歡迎港姐」都拿不到令他們心心不忿。有網友製作圖表加上超專業的數據分析指出獎項根本不應由10號張寶欣獲得，獲獎的該是9號金美黎，指比賽有不公之嫌。 <br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀: <strong>香港01【港姐2017】張寶欣Big Big Channel心心疑造假　金美黎輸得唔抵</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F116762%2F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%902017-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E6%AC%A3Big-Big-Channel%E5%BF%83%E5%BF%83%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E9%87%91%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%BE%97%E5%94%94%E6%8A%B5&d=5v2X%2F3V4BzXuJH62QZmuu8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5180c63c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加映: TVB高層余詠珊最權威回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>有網民質疑網上投票「最受歡迎香港小姐」，賽前是⑨金美黎累積最多心心，但最後是⑩張寶欣奪獎？余詠珊稱張寶欣賽前累積加臨場獲200多萬心心，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對不能造假</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n嘩,真係好合理好公道喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要問只要信,講咩就係咩架啦,你地邊個敢質疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>絕對</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不能</strong></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>造假</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0e43af147bf97dd83e248183fc82445c1f3e01","tid":395611,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/224303_20203bfa1fe3ea21a492218199d5675c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F224303_20203bfa1fe3ea21a492218199d5675c.jpg&h=4d13991f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/225439_f8b38409d45cd1ca31a9cb7ae3b0002e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F201